Title: The Influence
Writer: Ramsey Campbell, Michel Gaztambide, Daniel Rissech, Denis Rovira van Boekholt
Actors: Manuela Vellés, Maggie Civantos, Alain Hernández, Claudia Placer
Plot: After moving back to her family home to care for her dying mother, a nurse haunted by her childhood memories must struggle with an evil force in the house.
